messages.speech:
The Mission would focus on:

1)  Establishing 3 mega cities and 10 smart cities;
2)  Develop a roadmap for sustainable urban development by improving transportation, housing, expanding
      opportunities and living standards;
3)  Financial resource mobilization strategies for sustainable urban development;
4)  Solid waste management and treatment of wastewater;
5)  Pedestrian and cycling friendly clean and green urban spaces.
